snippet.title: The Fancy Pants Adventures - Launch Trailer
snippet.description: Run Fast. Run Fancy. The Fancy Pants Adventures is the definitive action-adventure platformer that you can play with your friends. Race through levels while stomping and slashing enemies with 40 weapons and an arsenal of moves, then battle it out in King of the Hill tournaments! Out now on XBLA and PSN!
